<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">We Need a Green New Deal to Defeat Fascism and Reverse Inequality</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<noscript><img width="1200" height="800" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-1200x800.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt='A protester wearing a shirt reading "GOOD JOBS AND A LIVABLE FUTURE" is carried away by cops' itemprop="url" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-200x133.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-400x267.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-800x533.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"></noscript><img width="1200" height="800" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%203%202'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt='A protester wearing a shirt reading "GOOD JOBS AND A LIVABLE FUTURE" is carried away by cops' itemprop="url" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-200x133.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-400x267.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-800x533.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal.jpg 2400w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0710-green-new-deal-1200x800.jpg" loading="lazy">
