<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/aocs-green-new-deal-is-just-the-start-next-lets-make-it-global/">AOC&#8217;s Green New Deal Is Just the Start. Next Let&#8217;s Make It Global.</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">The U.S. needs to play a chief role in spurring a global Green New Deal alongside a domestic one.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
