<article class="row hentry post-260061 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-interview tag-climate-crisis tag-fascism tag-green-new-deal tag-inequality tag-neoliberalism tag-renewable-energy section-environment-and-health primary_topic-environment" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ReportageNewsArticle">
